Python Dependencies
-------------------

The following Python packages are used by the notebook and utility module.
All are permissively licensed and compatible with MIT-0:

- boto3 (Apache-2.0) - AWS SDK for Python
- sagemaker (Apache-2.0) - Amazon SageMaker Python SDK
- matplotlib (PSF-based, BSD-compatible) - Plotting library
- pandas (BSD-3-Clause) - Data manipulation library
- Pillow (HPND, MIT-like) - Image processing library
- requests (Apache-2.0) - HTTP library
- huggingface-hub (Apache-2.0) - HuggingFace model download CLI (used in Dockerfile)
